{"tid":28955,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"注意！警方明起一連5日票控亂過馬路行人","createTime":"2016-12-08T09:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T09:43:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5967166c3cbbf4e1c6ab7a986e356b90c39573","tid":28955,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"警方明日起至下周二（13日），將票控亂過馬路或干犯嚴重違例事項的行人。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，將進行為期5天的全港行人道路安全行動，行動期間，警方將進行執法，票控亂過馬路或干犯嚴重違例事項的行人。各警察總區道路安全組人員在行動前，已在全港多個地點派發宣傳單張，加強行人對道路安全的意識及呼籲市民遵守交通規則。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，行人通常違反的規則包括不遵守交通燈號、在距離行人過路設施15米範圍內而不使用該些設施橫過馬路，及攀越路邊圍欄或穿過中央分道帶進入車路等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161208/s00001/1481170202006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161208%2Fs00001%2F1481170202006&d=iZ1a9SmCMlNlwUAqsoevFH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=7444f3e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161208%2Fs00001%2F1481170202006&h=58e42af6\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161208/s00001/1481170202006</a>"},{"pid":"124a8ccaa45f3d07b4d63d67f3439866a431b5c8","tid":28955,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:17:21.000Z","msg":"聽過gogovan 個司機講累警係換新告票所以年尾急住清舊貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bcc8d6426816289627b53940271bcc3e76b5fc","tid":28955,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"又來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e180d7bbe909fc7eb9cfc108871d35d10bd1a38","tid":28955,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef85dd74d258e3ce106a2f06b9ccd241256c6073","tid":28955,"uid":36551,"like":0